Fix dashboard UI and configure dark mode

Fix dashboard UI and configure dark mode
Add real-time metrics fetching and error handling to the dashboard, improve loading states, and update profile management.
* **Dashboard Component (`app/dashboard/page.tsx`)** - Add `useEffect` to fetch real-time metrics from the backend. - Update state with fetched metrics data. - Display fetched metrics in the `Dashboard` component. - Add loading and error states for better user experience.
* **Traffic Flow Component (`app/dashboard/traffic-flow/page.tsx`)** - Add loading state for API requests. - Display loading indicator in the `Traffic Flow` component.
* **Profile Component (`app/dashboard/profile/page.tsx`)** - Allow users to update their profile information and skin color. - Add state management for first name, last name, email, job title, and organization. - Implement profile update logic in the `handleSubmit` function.
* **Theme Provider (`components/theme-provider.tsx`)** - Add `useEffect` to handle hydration mismatch issues. - Ensure consistent rendering by setting a mounted state.
* **Devcontainer Configuration** - Add `.devcontainer/devcontainer.json` with tasks to install dependencies and run the development server.
